            <lg xml:id="TK543">
<l>antaṇar nūṟku maṟattiṟku mātiyāy </l>
<l> niṉṟatu maṉṉavaṉ kōl</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sceptre of the king is the firm support of the Vedas of the Brahmin, and of all virtues therein described.</l>
